# 没e也能玩

![](/assets/images/wp/2024/week5/meieyenengwang_1.png)

```





from gmpy2 import *
from Crypto.Util.number import *
def rsa(dp,dq,p,q,c):
    m1=pow(c,dp,p)
    m2=pow(c,dq,q)
    p_q=invert(p,q)
    m=m1+p_q*((m2-m1)%q)*p
    print(long_to_bytes(m))
rsa(dp,dq,p,q,c)
```
